overview: Staple-Man returns to Rhyneston, stronger than ever. However, this time, the city is in constant fear under the reining power of crime lord, Nutri-Gra-Mom. Without the presence of her arch enemy, her power has become seemingly unstoppable. With the help of Police Commissioner Gorgon, Staple-Man will try to do just that in this action-packed, tear-jerking masterpiece.
title: Staple-Man Rises
